{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/steven-spielberg-buktikan-dirinya-masih-raja-box-office-dengan-ready-player-one/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Steven Spielberg Buktikan Dirinya Masih Raja Box Office dengan “Ready Player One”","content":"<p><strong>Oleh: @HarryRezqiano</strong></p>\n<p>Ada beberapa hal yang ‘terjamin’ di dunia. Gula rasanya dijamin manis. Air laut pasti rasanya asin. Harga Bahan Bakar Minyak selalu tidak stabil. Dan Steven Spielberg membuat film yang akhirnya jadi <em>Box Office</em> di mana-mana.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45625\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45625\" data-attachment-id=\"45625\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steven-spielberg-buktikan-dirinya-masih-raja-box-office-dengan-ready-player-one/attachment/stev1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Steven Spielberg. (Sumber gambar: Entertainment Weekly)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Steven Spielberg. (Sumber gambar: Entertainment Weekly)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45625\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev1.jpg\" alt=\"Steven Spielberg. (Sumber gambar: Entertainment Weekly)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45625\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Steven Spielberg. (Sumber gambar: Entertainment Weekly)</p></div></p>\n<p>Hal itu rasanya tidak terlalu berlebihan karena dalam perjalanan karirnya Steven Spielberg memang jarang gagal menaklukkan Box Office dengan film-film dimana dia terlibat dalam pembuatannya. Baik itu sebagai sutradara, produser atau penulis naskah.  Atau menjadi semuanya sekaligus. Dengan karir perfilman yang membentang panjang selama lebih dari empat dekade, Steven Spielberg adalah tonggak penting era “<em>New Hollywood</em>” ; era kebangkitan modern perfilman Hollywood sejak 1960an hingga awal-awal 1980an.</p>\n<p>Steven Spielberg tidak terpaku dan mengkhususkan diri di satu genre film saja. Walau suka tidak suka namanya lebih mentereng jika diasosiasikan dengan genre fiksi ilmiah.</p>\n<p><em>Jaws</em> (1975 | US$470 Juta), <em>Close Encounters of the Third Kind</em> (1977 | US$306 Juta) serta <em>E.T the Extra-Terrestrial</em> (1982 | US$793 Juta) adalah beberapa dari film fiksi ilmiah dimana Steven Spielberg terlibat di dalamnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45626\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45626\" data-attachment-id=\"45626\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steven-spielberg-buktikan-dirinya-masih-raja-box-office-dengan-ready-player-one/attachment/stev2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Film tentang UFO. (Sumber gambar: TheFourOhFive)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Film tentang UFO. (Sumber gambar: TheFourOhFive)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45626\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev2.jpg\" alt=\"Film tentang UFO. (Sumber gambar: TheFourOhFive)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45626\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Film tentang UFO. (Sumber gambar: TheFourOhFive)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dalam perjalanannya, Spielberg juga membuat film-film bertema humanis dan ‘sensitif’ seperti kisah di era perbudakan, politik, peperangan bersejarah hingga tema arkelologi yang berbalut komedi aksi.</p>\n<p><em>Schindler’s List</em> (1993 | US$321 Juta) dan <em>Saving Private Ryan</em> (1998 | US$481 Juta) merupakan film-film Spielberg yang menggambarkan tentang getirnya situasi <em>World War</em> II. Kedua film ini diganjar Piala Oscar sebagai Film Terbaik.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45627\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45627\" data-attachment-id=\"45627\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steven-spielberg-buktikan-dirinya-masih-raja-box-office-dengan-ready-player-one/attachment/stev3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: HHSRampages\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: HHSRampages&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45627\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev3.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: HHSRampages\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45627\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: HHSRampages</p></div></p>\n<p>Sementara tetralogi <em>Indiana Jones</em> (1981 – 2008 | lebih dari US$1.9 Milyar) adalah satu dari <em>franchise</em> yang melambungkan serta menjaga posisi Harrison Ford di jajaran top elite aktor Hollywood selama berpuluh-puluh tahun.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45628\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45628\" data-attachment-id=\"45628\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steven-spielberg-buktikan-dirinya-masih-raja-box-office-dengan-ready-player-one/attachment/stev4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber gambar: Amazon)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber gambar: Amazon)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45628\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev4.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber gambar: Amazon)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45628\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Amazon</p></div></p>\n<p>Dan siapa yang bisa lupa dengan film fiksi ilmiah <em>Jurassic Park</em> (1993 | US$1.029 Milyar) ?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45629\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45629\" data-attachment-id=\"45629\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steven-spielberg-buktikan-dirinya-masih-raja-box-office-dengan-ready-player-one/attachment/stev5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: RoyalAlbertHall\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: RoyalAlbertHall&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45629\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev5.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: RoyalAlbertHall\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45629\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: RoyalAlbertHall</p></div></p>\n<p>Film yang diangkat dari novel laris berjudul sama karangan Michael Crichton itu merupakan film fiksi ilmiah sukses yang mampu menimbulkan pertanyaan (dan perdebatan) soal “bolehkah manusia coba-coba menjadi Tuhan dengan mengendalikan jalan kehidupan makhluk hidup yang sudah punah seperti Dinosaurus dengan proses kloning?”.</p>\n<p>Rasanya kita semua pernah menonton film Jurassic Park minimal sekali. Paling tidak di televisi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45630\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45630\" data-attachment-id=\"45630\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steven-spielberg-buktikan-dirinya-masih-raja-box-office-dengan-ready-player-one/attachment/stev6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Mendengar raungannya bikin bergidik. (Sumber gambar: LiveScience)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Mendengar raungannya bikin bergidik. (Sumber gambar: LiveScience)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45630\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev6.jpg\" alt=\"Mendengar raungannya bikin bergidik. (Sumber gambar: LiveScience)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45630\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mendengar raungannya bikin bergidik. (Sumber gambar: LiveScience)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dengan sederet reputasi mentereng seperti itu jelas ekspektasi serupa datang untuk film “<em>Ready Player One</em>” di mana Steve Spielberg kembali duduk di kursi sutradara selain sebagai produser film.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45631\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45631\" data-attachment-id=\"45631\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steven-spielberg-buktikan-dirinya-masih-raja-box-office-dengan-ready-player-one/attachment/stev7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber gambar: RoadToVR)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber gambar: RoadToVR)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45631\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev7.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber gambar: RoadToVR)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45631\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: RoadToVR</p></div></p>\n<p>Film ini, seperti halnya Jurassic Park, diadaptasi dari novel berjudul sama karangan Ernest Cline yang juga bertindak sebagai penulis naskah di film ini. Berlatar di masa depan (tahun 2045, yang tidak terlalu jauh dari masa kini) <em>Ready Player One</em> sudah memancing rasa penasaran dan jadi <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengupas-trailer-ready-player-one-yang-seru-banget/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">bahan pembicaraan bahkan sejak trailer resminya dirilis ke pasaran</a>.</p>\n<p>Dengan referensi pop culture sejak era 80an, film <em>Ready Player One</em> seakan-akan diciptakan untuk menggoyang urat syaraf sentimental penonton akan berbagai jenis dan ragam referensi pop culture dunia. Mulai dari film hingga <em>video game.</em> Apalagi tema film ini pada dasarnya adalah <em>video game “Virtual Reality</em>”. Sesuatu yang saat ini sudah ada di luar sana dan bisa jadi trend jika dikelola dengan tepat dan harganya terjangkau.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45632\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45632\" data-attachment-id=\"45632\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steven-spielberg-buktikan-dirinya-masih-raja-box-office-dengan-ready-player-one/attachment/stev8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Peralatan VR sudah mulai diproduksi saat ini. (Sumber gambar: MyVue)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Peralatan VR sudah mulai diproduksi saat ini. (Sumber gambar: MyVue)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45632\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev8.jpg\" alt=\"Peralatan VR sudah mulai diproduksi saat ini. (Sumber gambar: MyVue)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stev8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45632\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Peralatan VR sudah mulai diproduksi saat ini. (Sumber gambar: MyVue)</p></div></p>\n<p>Film <em>Ready Player One</em> beredar di seluruh dunia sejak 29 Maret 2018 dan sampai saat ini sudah menghasilkan US$181 Juta. Jangan bayangkan angka ini akan mentok disana, karena masa pemutaran <em>Ready Player One</em> di bioskop masih panjang. Angka final <em>Box Office</em> dari <em>Ready Player One</em> sama sekali belum bisa diprediksi.</p>\n<p>Apakah Ready Player One akan kembali membuktikan kesaktian seorang Steven Spielberg dalam menyajikan sebuah film Box Office fiksi ilmiah yang seru, penuh imajinasi dan <em>memorable</em>? Buat kamu yang belum nonton, intip dulu aja review-nya <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ready-player-one-film-dengan-nuansa-pop-culture-yang-kental/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">di sini</a>. Siapa tahu bisa jadi bahan pertimbangan?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"b08efd96-3cee-5253-bb4f-5797ac6bde03"}}}